---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="About | Eauxptim"
  description="About Eauxptim and its mission in water and wastewater process optimization."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>About Eauxptim</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Eauxptim is focused on research, engineering, and software development
        for advanced optimization of water and wastewater processes.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow prose">
      <h2>What we stand for</h2>
      <p>
        Eauxptim brings together technical knowledge in hydric processes with
        modern digital tools such as software platforms, AI-enabled solutions,
        digital twins, sensors, and algorithms.
      </p>

      <p>
        The objective is practical impact: improving treatment performance,
        reducing inefficiencies, strengthening operational insight, and enabling
        more intelligent control and decision-making.
      </p>

      <h2>Our approach</h2>
      <p>
        We work at the interface of applied engineering and digital innovation.
        This includes technical consulting, process studies, software
        development, modelling, and collaborative R&D.
      </p>

      <h2>Typical project areas</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Water and wastewater treatment optimization</li>
        <li>Digital twin design and deployment</li>
        <li>Process modelling and algorithm development</li>
        <li>AI-assisted monitoring and decision support</li>
        <li>Technical audit, control, and engineering advisory</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>